name: testNoLoggingAfterChangingPassword
description: TC_01.001.17 Validate No Logging Old Password After Changing Password
descriptionHtml: TC_01.001.17 Validate No Logging Old Password After Changing Password

testStage.description: TC_01.001.17 Validate No Logging Old Password After Changing Password

steps.name: Enter email address in the email field
Enter password in the password field
Click on the 'Profile' button that appears
Enter the password in the 'Current password' field
Enter the NEW password in the 'New password' field
Enter the NEW password in the 'New password (again)' field
Click on the 'Change your password' button
Click on the 'Logout' on the sidebar
Enter email address in the email field
Enter password in the password field
User should not be allowed to login
